mixin article(imgs)
  .col-md-6.mt-2.mt-md-4
    .row.height-card.border.rounded
      a.col-5.image-card(href='#' style='background-image: url("https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/400/0*' + imgs[0] + '")')
      .col-7.card-block.py-3
        a.d-block.no-hover.height-card-block.mb-1(href='#')
          .card-title.h4.text-dark.crop-text.crop-text-2.mb-1.mb-md-2 Suspendisse Vel Enim Vitae, Tellus Faucibus Iaculis
          .card-text
            .small.text-success.text-truncate.mb-1.mb-md-2 https://mylink.test.com/article/a-title-of-some-link
            .text-body.crop-text.crop-text-3.
              Curabitur aliquet nisl libero, sit amet varius mauris iaculis nec. Aliquam erat volutpat. Mauris non auctor nibh.
              Nam pellentesque convallis velit vel posuere. Maecenas tristique nulla in nulla malesuada mollis.
        .d-flex.flex-row
          .pr-2
            a(href='#')
              img.border.rounded-circle.avatar-small(src='https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/fit/c/80/80/' + imgs[1])
          .px-0.crop-text-block
            .small.text-truncate
              a(href='#') Johny Stratuss Anntjel Majetkwonlooyk
            .small.crop-text.crop-text-2 Fab 19
              i.fas.fa-circle.dotsmall.align-middle.px-1
              | 704 bookmarks
          .pl-1.flex-fill
            a.float-right.text-body(href='#')
              i.far.fa-bookmark.font-09

